      "review_summary": "The branch adds OpenCode Go Zen-balance-only fallback behavior and tests, extends OpenCode Go snapshot rendering, adds a release-note entry, and adds a PR-specific CI artifact job.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR defects: source inspection shows includeZenBalance is controlled by context.includeOptionalUsage and requiredZenBalanceFallback rethrows when the task is nil. Live reproduction of the intended Zen-only account success path is still missing from the PR evidence.",
